summary: Your house is added under Dragon Bridge.
descriptionHtml:
----------------
Dragon Bridge Players House (v1.0)
----------------

Your house is added under Dragon Bridge.

Please be sure to back up your save file.


---
Author : hdela


---
This mod was built with Skyrim US Ver 1.7.7.0.x

Master files : Skyrim.esm, Update.esm


---
Installation : Unzip the file, and overwrite Skyrim Data folder. Or drop the esp into your Skyrim Data directory.


---
Ver: 1.0

Single bed x4
No respawn container x35

Alchemy Workbench
Enchanting Workbench
Smelter Marker
BlackSmith Forge
Armor Workbench 
Blacksmith Sharpening Wheel
Tanning Rack Marker
Cooking Pot

Guard Dog
Guard Fish x2


---
Enjoy!

by hdela
